# Reference Examples

This folder contains grayscale sensor reference examples.

Rules:
1. These files are read-only reference code.
2. Do not compile these files into the main Keil project.
3. Do not copy ti_msp_dl_config.c/h or empty.syscfg from examples into the main project.
4. Do not copy main.c, empty.c, SysTick_Handler, GROUP1_IRQHandler directly.
5. Only extract ADC reading, calibration, binarization, and error calculation logic.
6. All pins and peripherals must be configured in the main project's empty.syscfg.